<p>Here are screenshots of comparison of <strong>our</strong> outputted video vs.&nbsp;<strong>Sayatoo’s</strong> vs.&nbsp;<strong>H265 common</strong>. # Our Format<br>
<img src="https://bowen951209.github.io/bowen-blog/posts/trans_video/formatOfOurs.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="ours"></p>
