<section id="why-i-wrote-this-post" class="level1">
<h1>Why I wrote this post?</h1>
<p>I am working on <a href="https://github.com/Bowen951209/open-karaoke-toolkit">a karaoke software project</a>, being confused about exporting a transparent video. In the end, I referenced the Sayatoo, the commercial karaoke software and found that it strangely used PNG as its video input. After a lot of attempts and I finally found that you have to use PNG codec for transparent videos, so that PowerDirector can recognize it.</p>
